# Backend Architecture

## Structure
- [src/index.ts](mdc:backend/src/index.ts) - Entry point that starts the Express server
- [src/app.ts](mdc:backend/src/app.ts) - Express app configuration
- [src/routes](mdc:backend/src/routes) - API route definitions
- [src/controllers](mdc:backend/src/controllers) - Request handlers
- [src/models](mdc:backend/src/models) - Database models
- [src/seed](mdc:backend/src/seed) - Database seed scripts

## Key Patterns
- Express with TypeScript
- SQLite database with custom models
- RESTful API endpoints
- MVC architecture (Models, Controllers, Routes)

